    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Exceptional mint-condition example being represented honestly. The exterior presents beautifully with excellent paint, trim, and finish, the interior is extremely clean and well-kept, and the overall car shows the kind of care buyers hope to find but rarely do. It should impress immediately in person and is the sort of standout, top-tier car that needs little to no excuse.",
